Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So does that mean...I have to whittle 16 down to 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? We'll be living together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,765)}Living together...
