Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"These sixteen girls before you are aiming to become idols."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"You, Kuro-chan, are tasked with selecting the members..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"...and producing your own idol group."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.89,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You know this guy\Nis gonna fall for them.
