Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kuro-chan really does love idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows every little detail, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Literally everything. Any live show he goes to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...he takes his notebook, and writes every single thing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Creepy.  That's just creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why, this time, Kuro-chan will be becoming an idol producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.87,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He'll be producing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be producing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Just watching this creeped me out.
