Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had auditions, sure, but we were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's like that, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.45,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Imagine having Kuro-chan as a producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume that it was left out that they would be produced by Kuro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.  The sixteen hopefuls were only told...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...that this was an idol audition for TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't tell them it was Wednesday Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So that what those sixteen knew when applying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all they knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you told them that Kuro-chan would be the producer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...I think a lot of them would have just quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.97,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If we told them they can just leave when they want...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...there wouldn't be anyone left.
