Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.  But I wouldn't want to be in their shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, they know if they leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're giving up the chance to appear on primetime TV.
