Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, towards the end I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...he may be able to pull off making an idol group, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...he's way too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:09.63,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He is going quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He is blazing through!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:11.57,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It was like that from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was going to end in that silence...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.37,0:24:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...but then suddenly that girl is shrieking "aaaah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:17.59,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.79,0:24:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What even was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:18.38,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\clip(312,989,636,1080)}Was something stuck down their throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.38,0:24:20.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Was something stuck down their throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying someone was choking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So what kind of company is this "WACK"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.87,0:24:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They have groups like "BiSH".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.45,0:24:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They create a somewhat different kind of idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.85,0:24:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They get to be their real selves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.73,0:24:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you think having a group produced by Kuro-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.33,0:24:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...is the kind of thing WACK does?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It saddens me to say, but you would be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.97,0:24:46.41,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.61,0:24:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigemori, what did you think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.17,0:24:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get over the cringeyness of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.55,0:24:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...it....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.47,0:24:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.61,0:24:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It became the opposite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.23,0:24:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes full circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.58,0:25:00.35,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Once you're over it, you have the feeling of euphoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.35,0:25:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! It made me want to watch even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.72,0:25:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.27,0:25:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so fun!  It's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.26,0:25:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by WACKisIDOL.

